CVSSearch
=========


INSTALLATION
============

* install the latest release of the sleepycat database from
  http://www.sleepycat.com/download.html  
 
  From the dist/ directory, type

    ./configure --enable-cxx
    make 
    make install

* install the latest version of omsee from 
  ftp://ftp.omsee.com/pub/unstable/nightly/latest/

  ./configure
  make 
  make install

* now configure CVSSearch, compile, and install:

  ./configure
  make
  make install




Building a CVSSearch Database
=============================

setenv CVSROOT ... (location of CVS repository)
setenv CVSDATA ... (location of CVSSearch database to be built)

cvsbuild -f dir.list [ dir.list is a list of directories in CVS
                       repository to index ]



